      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions must demonstrably replicate the physical test fixture constraints as specified in ASTM F1717 Section 8.",
      "rationale": "Fixed-fixed boundary conditions in the FEA replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture. Fixture compliance was measured and incorporated as a spring stiffness (k=12,400 N/mm) at the upper grip. Equivalency confirmed at level 2."
